{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b5cb41d9925324fa4c14866fee7457ad/2a52b/lier-cast.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 38.07439824945295%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Koning Lier Cast\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b5cb41d9925324fa4c14866fee7457ad/a111b/lier-cast.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b5cb41d9925324fa4c14866fee7457ad/aca85/lier-cast.jpg 163w,\n/static/b5cb41d9925324fa4c14866fee7457ad/0954f/lier-cast.jpg 325w,\n/static/b5cb41d9925324fa4c14866fee7457ad/a111b/lier-cast.jpg 650w,\n/static/b5cb41d9925324fa4c14866fee7457ad/2a52b/lier-cast.jpg 914w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>Naast programmeren doe ik ook aan toneelspelen en theater. Bij dit project kwamen beidde talenten aan bod. </p>\n<p>Ik speelde een rol in Koning Lier, naar Shakespeare's <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/King_Lear\">King Lear</a>, van amateur gezelschap <a href=\"http://knapschiedam.nl\">Knap Schiedam</a> en ik heb het ticket reserveringssysteem op de website geprogrammeerd. </p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/41ba1754bb9c8898e2d070e69029cd37/79fe0/lier-flyer.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 431px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 74.94199535962876%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"flyer koning lier\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/41ba1754bb9c8898e2d070e69029cd37/79fe0/lier-flyer.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/41ba1754bb9c8898e2d070e69029cd37/aca85/lier-flyer.jpg 163w,\n/static/41ba1754bb9c8898e2d070e69029cd37/0954f/lier-flyer.jpg 325w,\n/static/41ba1754bb9c8898e2d070e69029cd37/79fe0/lier-flyer.jpg 431w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Koning Lier: Acteren en programmeren","date":"2018-05-23","category":"Theatre"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/Acteren-en-programmeren/"}}